The '''Hardan plague''' was a virulent disease known to be transported by [[Bogan's brown nafen]]. An outbreak which killed 98% of the population on [[Dagelin Minor]] was traced back to a shipment of nafen that was imported to control the [[Dhuru fly]] population.

